==== Novel Peripheral Biomarkers

    - Hair growth rate (baseline vs.\ 3-month follow-up): measured as new hair emergence from scalp
    - Nail growth rate: fingernail and toenail length change over 3 months
    - Baseline metabolic rate: indirect calorimetry in resting state
    - Resting muscle ATP: quantified via magnetic resonance spectroscopy (MRS) of vastus lateralis

